annotation: The first construction phase of the 100-MW Gansu Jiayuguan Solar Park finishes.
title: Solar photovoltaic capacity
moreinfo: Renewable solar power has vast potential to help meet global energy demands with exponentially increasing global production in recent years. The International Energy Agency (IEA) estimates that solar power could provide for as much as 11% of global electricity production by 2050.
